book.title: Love's Prisoner (Wyndham Werewolf #1)
book.description: Storyline: Love's Prisoner (Wyndham Werewolf #1) \n Trapped in an elevator, Jeannie Lawrence experienced unwilling rapture at Michael Windham's hands. She never expected the devilishly handsome man to show back up in her life  or turn out to be a werewolf! Will she accept her destiny to be his mate?\n
book.author: MaryJanice Davidson
